    },
    {
        "strip-and-raft foundations": "Strip-And-Raft Foundations"
    },
    {
        ". Until the 18th century, however, no theoretical basis for soil design had been developed and the discipline was more of an art than a science, relying on past experience.      Several foundation-related engineering problems, such as the ": null
    },
    {
        "Leaning Tower of Pisa": "Leaning Tower Of Pisa"
