    {
        ", and ": null
    },
    {
        "photogrammetry": "Photogrammetry"
    },
    {
        "; or it can be as simple as an engineer walking around to observe the physical conditions at the site. Geologic mapping and interpretation of geomorphology are typically completed in consultation with a ": null
    },
    {
        "geologist": "Geologist"
    },
    {
